ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisRAINY RIVER FIRST NATIONS SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of an amount equal to the GST payable on land if it is purchased by or for the Rainy River First Nations in Ontario and set apart as a reserve under the terms of a tripartite Settlement Agreement.
